flowchart TD
    Start([START]) --> Init[Set attempts to zero and mark user as not verified]
    Init --> InsertCard[/Display: Please insert your card/]
    InsertCard --> AuthLoop{Have there been fewer than 3 attempts AND is the user still unverified?}
    
    AuthLoop -->|YES| ReadPIN[/Ask user to enter PIN/]
    AuthLoop -->|NO| AuthCheck{Is the user still unverified?}
    
    ReadPIN --> PinCheck{Is the PIN correct?}
    PinCheck -->|YES| SetAuth[Mark the user as successfully verified]
    PinCheck -->|NO| IncAttempts[Add 1 to the failed attempts counter]
    IncAttempts --> PrintWrong[/Display: Incorrect PIN/]
    
    SetAuth --> AuthLoop
    PrintWrong --> AuthLoop
    
    AuthCheck -->|YES| BlockCard[/Display: Card Blocked. Please contact your bank/]
    BlockCard --> EndSession[/Display: Please take your card. Have a good day/]
    
    AuthCheck -->|NO| InitTrans[Prepare to start the transaction session]
    InitTrans --> TransLoop{Does the user want to continue with transactions?}
    
    TransLoop -->|NO| EndSession
    TransLoop -->|YES| ReadBal[/Retrieve the current account balance/]
    
    ReadBal --> PrintBal[/Show the user their current balance/]
    PrintBal --> ReadAmount[/Ask the user for the withdrawal amount/]
    
    ReadAmount --> CheckBal{Is the requested amount greater than the balance?}
    
    CheckBal -->|YES| PrintNoFunds[/Display: Insufficient balance/]
    CheckBal -->|NO| CheckMod{Is the amount NOT a multiple of 20TL?}
    
    CheckMod -->|YES| PrintModErr[/Display: Error - Amount must be in units of 20TL/]
    CheckMod -->|NO| CheckLimit{Does the amount exceed the daily limit?}
    
    CheckLimit -->|YES| PrintLimitErr[/Display: Error - Daily withdrawal limit reached/]
    CheckLimit -->|NO| DispenseCash[Update the account balance and the daily limit]
    DispenseCash --> PrintReceipt[/Dispense the cash and print the receipt/]
    
    PrintNoFunds --> AskContinue[/Display: Would you like to perform another transaction?/]
    PrintModErr --> AskContinue
    PrintLimitErr --> AskContinue
    PrintReceipt --> AskContinue
    
    AskContinue --> ReadChoice[/Get the user's choice: YES or NO/]
    ReadChoice --> CheckChoice{Did the user choose NO?}
    
    CheckChoice -->|YES| SetContFalse[End the transaction session]
    CheckChoice -->|NO| TransLoop
    
    SetContFalse --> TransLoop
    
    EndSession --> End([END])
